<cb:div type="xuzang-notes">
<head>卍續藏 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0567b05" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0567b05">勝會明宗令終為美法座將散令各說悟廣釋眾迷固宜致問哉</note>
<note n="0567b06" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0567b06">滅者滅生耳若悟無生滅何所滅即無生法忍也</note>
<note n="0567b07" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0567b07">我所我之有也法既無我誰有所也</note>
<note n="0567b08" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0567b08">有漏五陰名受無漏名不受悟法本空二俱不受則無得無行</note>
<note n="0567b09" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0567b09">淨生于垢實性無垢淨何所淨</note>
<note n="0567b10" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0567b10">惑心微起為動取相深著為念言一欲以去二不言一也言無欲以去有不言無也何有于二</note>
<note n="0567b11" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0567b11">世間三界也出世間無漏道品法也出義生于入無入生死故無出世間</note>
<note n="0567b12" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0567b12">縛然生死之別名</note>
<note n="0567b13" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0567b13">有為虗偽法無常故名盡實相無為法常住故不盡</note>
<note n="0568b01" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0568b01">見我實性者我本自無而況非我也</note>
<note n="0568b02" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0568b02">見無明性即為是明若見明為明即是無明故不可取</note>
<note n="0568b03" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0568b03">色即是空不待色滅然後為空</note>
<note n="0568b04" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0568b04">四種四大也空種空大也然四大之性無前後中無異空大也</note>
<note n="0568b05" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0568b05">悟六情為性則六塵不起三毒為寂滅道</note>
<note n="0568b06" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0568b06">以六度為妙因迴向一切智者二也若悟因果同性入于一相乃應不二</note>
<note n="0568b07" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0568b07">三行雖異俱是無緣解脫</note>
<note n="0568b08" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0568b08">有相則有對有則為二不繫一與二故不二</note>
<note n="0568b09" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0568b09">諸法生時空生滅時空滅身存身亡亦何異而懷驚惧乎</note>
<note n="0568b10" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0568b10">三業雖殊無作一也</note>
<note n="0568b11" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0568b11">因我故有彼二名所以生見我實相者不起彼我識</note>
<note n="0568b12" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0568b12">得在我相在彼我不得相誰取誰捨</note>
<note n="0568b13" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0568b13">六根盡廢心想都滅雖經晝夜不覺晦明即無闇明耳</note>
<note n="0568b14" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0568b14">世間無縛曷為而厭涅槃無解曷為而樂</note>
<note n="0568b15" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0568b15">雖曰無見而無所不見此真慧眼之體</note>
<note n="0568b16" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0568b16">諸菩薩各說不二之義似有不二可說是以文殊明無可說為不二</note>
<note n="0569b01" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0569b01">文殊以無言無說無示無識是未明說為無說也所以維摩默然</note>
<note n="0569b02" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0569b02">語默雖殊明宗一也有言于無言未若無言于無言默然之論論之妙也</note>
</p>
